{"tid":1334611,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"頭先係台灣龍山寺幫香港求左支籤","createTime":"2019-07-20T07:25:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-20T07:49:19.000Z","uid":82387,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"b1a0972928cbb3ffcf23625ffdeae06f62bd8ac8","tid":1334611,"uid":82387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T07:25:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xUbwTCv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxUbwTCv.png&h=cb1fa1d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇人可以幫手解下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37cbe02c0e42e73de34d1f327c01792db2df2fa1","tid":1334611,"uid":37964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T07:27:07.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"755259e79583e1829d5030b5f933cbf1f5b5cfff","tid":1334611,"uid":258703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T07:28:48.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"eb8e47870e6ee03f43434ea89fd8561c548c79ed","tid":1334611,"uid":37964,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T07:29:08.000Z","msg":"第六十一首：廝養卒走燕取歸趙王　　大吉<br />\n日上吟詩月下歌，逢場作戲笑呵呵　　<br />\n相逢會處難藏隱，喝采齊聲嗹哩囉 　<br />\n（四句淺釋：與佳人白天吟詩晚上唱歌，歡喜作樂笑開懷；在此相逢聚首無所不談，耳邊眾人的喝采聲連貫不絕，這樣的生活是很滿足快樂的啊。）<br />\n佳人在屋，唱吟詩曲，一片歡嘉，取樂且足。此籤佳人歡樂之象，凡事大吉如意。　<br />\n靈簽之曰：本簽之示於弟子曰。日上吟詩月下歌者。為佳人歡樂之象者。凡是百事興。大吉昌之徵。因時運知。所謀之事也。百事如意之時。惟將如此康泰上盈之道。何如保之。冤之。保之。方能克终。易言之。君之今也。佳人在屋唱。吟詩曲一片歡嘉取樂且足之佳境。 　　<br />\n交易－利　婚姻－成　求財－順　自身－吉利　家宅－安　六畜－旺　田蠶－熟　尋人－至　行人－至　六甲－生女　山墳－吉　訟詞－有理　疾病－即痊　失物－凶　移徒－吉<br />\n詳解：此籤有&rdquo;不可貌相&rdquo;之意。鼓勵當事人，要有自信。很多人常不甘安於現狀，覺得自己地位太低、人微言輕，因此無不想力爭上游，爬得越高越好。但俗云：&rdquo;三百六十行，行行出狀元&rdquo;。職位高低代表的只不過是一時的虛名，不一定非要苦苦追求。這個社會需要各式各樣的人，人人各司其職，才能保持平衡。應以自己的工作為榮，知福、惜福，安居樂業。切勿好高騖遠，豈不知慾望少一點，快樂就更多一點？另外，切勿輕視小看地位卑微的人，也許其中臥虎藏龍個個身懷絕技，只不過自己有眼不識泰山罷了！<br />\n<br />\n利申：上網鳩copy<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02578144699f549d76a7303ef15a6ba4edea7cea","tid":1334611,"uid":127929,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T07:29:31.000Z","msg":"想睇左手<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bd1c276c3c1b7e0cc214118c56f7f562a848067","tid":1334611,"uid":511,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"02578144699f549d76a7303ef15a6ba4edea7cea","tid":1334611,"uid":127929,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T07:29:31.000Z","msg":"想睇左手<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T07:30:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60808dcbf91caf06db733382712196e353db24f8","tid":1334611,"uid":73143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T07:32:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.0961223888.com/kannon/Kannon61.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.0961223888.com%2Fkannon%2FKannon61.htm&d=JxnBaozbJlL%2F%2BfT%2BMtMvbtey%2FoW3U1ZMpR7BmJTbZh4%3D&h=70ae3b74\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.0961223888.com/kannon/Kannon61.htm</a>"},{"pid":"a4c33f18956e7ccc0ff15455bacb840cc59860f4","tid":1334611,"uid":23635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T07:32:54.000Z","msg":"睇錯淫人妻女笑呵呵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a80125e0c2140850c5b87f744fcf6dba9b386bf5","tid":1334611,"uid":253016,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T07:34:29.000Z","msg":"若問 事情結果如何，本籤代表這是個可以喝采的結果。<br />\n若問事情該怎麼做，那把做人做好，此事即有好成果。<br />\n若問對這件事的態度與看法如何，那就是要樂觀、信心以對。<br />\n若能掌握以上原則，即使是小兵也能立大功<br />